21 IC 31-32-11-1, and IC 31-33-5, a school counselor is immune from
22 disclosing privileged or confidential communication made to the
23 counselor as a counselor by a student.
24 (b) Except as provided in IC 20-33-7.5, and IC 31-32-11-1, and
25 IC 31-33-5, the matters communicated are privileged and protected
26 against disclosure.
